name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Mystic Pixels: The Enigmatic Demon Mask Live Wallpaper

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Demon Mask Pixel live wallpaper with a clock and Google search bar, adding a retro vibe to your new tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Elevate your browser with the eerie allure of a pixel-style Demon Mask. This wallpaper combines retro vibes and functional tools like a clock and search bar for a unique browsing experience.

Extension Features
Pixel Art Design: Mystical Demon Mask with retro charm.
Clock Integration: Stay on schedule with ease.
Google Search: Instant access for efficient browsing.
Lightweight Performance: Smooth and optimized functionality.
